=Yuanming yuan 圓明園 Garden of perfect Brightness=
==Literature==
===PhD Dissertations===
* Hui Zou: The Jing of Line-Method: A Perspective Garden in the Garden of Round Brightness. McGill University, 2005
* John R. Finlay: "40 Views of the Yuanming yuan": Image and Ideology in a Qianlong Imperial Album of Poetry and Paintings. Yale University, 2011
===Monographs===
* Che Bing Chiu: Yuanming yuan: Le Jardin de la Clarte parfaite. Besançon: Les Éditions de l'Imprimeur, 2000
* Young-tsu Wong: A Paradise lost: The Imperial Garden Yuanming yuan. Honolulu: University of Hawai'i, 2001
* DInes Eben v Racknitz: Die Plünderung des Yuanming yuan: Imperiale Beutenahme im britisch-französischen Chinafeldzug von 1860. Brown, 2013